      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Clouds of Narwa Rumble Again",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "Worrying news indeed... Narwa\r\nhas been spotted in the Coral\r\nPalace. Fortunately, it has yet\r\nto meet up with its king, but\r\nI have a terrible feeling... Hunter,\r\nyou must leap into action at once.\r\nWe cannot allow them to reunite!",
